### get all data without pagination
### will return:  { full_name: '', email: '', token: '' }
GET {{url}}/all HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
# Authorization: {{token}}

### get single data
# @prompt id enter id
GET {{url}}/show/{{id}} HTTP/1.1
